snippet.title: Super Star Wars (1992) [SNES] Complete Playthrough
snippet.description:
Playthrough of the first game in the Super Star Wars trilogy for the Super Nintendo. Despite its difficulty level it's still one of the best Star Wars games ever made.

TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@dangermeat

About the game:
Super Star Wars is an action video game released in 1992 for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System based on the 1977 film Star Wars. Super Star Wars features side-scrolling run and gun gameplay, although it has stages which feature other challenges, such as driving a landspeeder or piloting an X-wing. It also features multiple playable characters with different abilities.

The game was followed by two sequels based on the subsequent Star Wars films, Super Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back (1993) and Super Star Wars: Return of the Jedi (1994).
